Q) @Order(HIGHEST_PRECEDENCE) to create bean fastly
@Component
@Order(Ordered.HIGHEST_PRECEDENCE)

Q) Optimistic vs Pessimistic Locking?
Ans: Optimistic: @version no lock in read High performance.
Pessimistic Locking: @Lock(PESSIMISTIC_Write) : wait for other thread to complete transaction strong consistency.

Q) Microservices design patterns?
Ans:Strangler pattern, SAGA pattern---> Sequence of local transactions ,CQRS-->Strangler,API Gateway

